<br />I ordered a pair of these connectors a couple weeks ago.  I found that if I centered the cart in the connector, the pins will connect as expected.  But it has to be centered, and even then it barely makes contact on the outside pins since the contacts on the cart have a 2.5mm pitch instead of 2.54mm.

		

